com.jaxio.celerio.template

Class TemplateExecution

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jaxio.celerio.template.TemplateExecution

  • public class TemplateExecution
extends Object
    The TemplateExecution is used from the template file ($output var) to:
    • configure where to write the evaluated template
    • manage java imports
    • abort the generation if needed

      • dynamicAnnotation

        public String dynamicAnnotation(String fullType)

      • dynamicAnnotationTakeOver

        public String dynamicAnnotationTakeOver(String... fullTypes)
        Import the passed fullTypes and returns the corresponding annotations (one per line). In case the current class is taken over by the user, the fullTypes are not imported and each annotation line returned is commented out. A comment informs the java developper that he should use these commented annotation in his subclass.
